{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Border Town was once a peaceful and tranquil paradise, but it has become a ruin due to the full-scale invasion of orcs. The villagers scattered in fear, leaving only an old man who remained, harboring hopes of rebuilding the village. One day, you unexpectedly faint in the forest by the town, thus beginning an adventure intertwined with the fate of it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN2.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u65b0\u7248\u91c7\u96c6.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore this world without restraint. Cross through different scenes such as jungles, wetlands, snowfields, and deserts, overcoming the unknown challenges brought by the alternation of day and night and the dark environments underground. Face threats from various fantastical creatures, encounter NPCs with different personalities, and experience one extraordinary story after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u65b0\u7248\u79cd\u5730.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN3.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u62db\u52df\u6751\u6c11.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After communicating with the villagers and building relationships, you can recruit them to join the team for the town\u2019s reconstruction. Each villager has a unique profession, ranging from farmers to miners, lumberjacks, and even bunny girls. And they will become important helpers in your efforts to build the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN4.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u65b0\u7248\u5efa\u9020.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players can choose to explore and play in this world freely in their preferred way, whether it\u2019s cultivating farmland, raising animals, chopping trees, mining, gathering resources, building houses, or even accepting guild commissions to hunt monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN5.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u5192\u9669\u6218\u6597.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features over 600 unique items, including various crops, equipment, tools, weapons, gears, and materials. Players can plant a vast array of crops and cook them into various delicacies, or create workbenches, build houses, equipping themselves with more powerful weapons to face the impending enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN6.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u65b0\u7248\u9a91\u4e58.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While managing the village, don\u2019t forget your primary duty as an adventurer! Head to the adventure guild to take on quests, prepare supplies, and traverse forests, snowfields, and deserts to eliminate monsters. Explore abandoned camps to find treasures, restore them as strongholds, and defeat goblin enemies, snowmen, and stonemen guarding the minerals. Purchase treasure maps to unlock clues, dig for hidden precious treasures around the world, and let the world know your adventure legend!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Emerging blacksmith","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/e9546aeae7b7093c00bfa1446baf2485a1c9a1e8.jpg"},{"name":"Forging Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/ba6975d8b02eeee83c3f9561fc409c694566e893.jpg"},{"name":"Alchemist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/a2746a22859083eef68b3240a7843c96731ffe6f.jpg"},{"name":"Master Craftsman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/b603383dafd931ac0b31744736a926e912d12098.jpg"},{"name":"Infrastructure construction","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/28d402f2bd0d355aa671c1be5dba7f276ef4e740.jpg"},{"name":"Beekeepers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/9efc002032908ea8fda7039d96c9963bedb3a80b.jpg"},{"name":"The beginning of legend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/420627380b9363e2222f0b5aec0710bde0040d25.jpg"},{"name":"Warm cabin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/7c61f494e95e2312fd6815f81c885ef016a277c6.jpg"},{"name":"New Green in the Field","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/b05a09c4f82dd8462eb4b984fe90c057a2109185.jpg"},{"name":"Tongue Feast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1967820/6f12bbe67a91d1e40684d1fea7059d9920bc30f4.jpg"}],"total":42},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1967820?t=1737945246","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737945246","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/6a196b77dbcd7bcdab1fb423d84eb48b873fdc43/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737945246","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/6a196b77dbcd7bcdab1fb423d84eb48b873fdc43/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737945246","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u82f1\u6587\u4e00\u56fe\u6d41new.png?t=1737945246\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Border Town was once a peaceful and tranquil paradise, but it has become a ruin due to the full-scale invasion of orcs. The villagers scattered in fear, leaving only an old man who remained, harboring hopes of rebuilding the village. One day, you unexpectedly faint in the forest by the town, thus beginning an adventure intertwined with the fate of it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN2.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u65b0\u7248\u91c7\u96c6.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore this world without restraint. Cross through different scenes such as jungles, wetlands, snowfields, and deserts, overcoming the unknown challenges brought by the alternation of day and night and the dark environments underground. Face threats from various fantastical creatures, encounter NPCs with different personalities, and experience one extraordinary story after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u65b0\u7248\u79cd\u5730.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN3.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u62db\u52df\u6751\u6c11.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After communicating with the villagers and building relationships, you can recruit them to join the team for the town\u2019s reconstruction. Each villager has a unique profession, ranging from farmers to miners, lumberjacks, and even bunny girls. And they will become important helpers in your efforts to build the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN4.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u65b0\u7248\u5efa\u9020.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players can choose to explore and play in this world freely in their preferred way, whether it\u2019s cultivating farmland, raising animals, chopping trees, mining, gathering resources, building houses, or even accepting guild commissions to hunt monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN5.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u5192\u9669\u6218\u6597.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features over 600 unique items, including various crops, equipment, tools, weapons, gears, and materials. Players can plant a vast array of crops and cook them into various delicacies, or create workbenches, build houses, equipping themselves with more powerful weapons to face the impending enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/EN6.png?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/\u65b0\u7248\u9a91\u4e58.gif?t=1737945246\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While managing the village, don\u2019t forget your primary duty as an adventurer! Head to the adventure guild to take on quests, prepare supplies, and traverse forests, snowfields, and deserts to eliminate monsters. Explore abandoned camps to find treasures, restore them as strongholds, and defeat goblin enemies, snowmen, and stonemen guarding the minerals. Purchase treasure maps to unlock clues, dig for hidden precious treasures around the world, and let the world know your adventure legend!</p>","developers":["GoHoGames"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/header.jpg?t=1737945246","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Linux<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel I3<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Integrated Graphics<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 512 MB available space</li